---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Case Studies - Donut Cove Consulting" 
  description="See how Donut Cove Consulting has helped businesses eliminate tedious tasks and improve employee satisfaction through custom software solutions."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center space-y-8">
        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-6xl">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-donut-dark-pink via-donut-dark-cyan to-donut-dark-moss bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Case Studies
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Real results from real businesses. See how we've helped teams focus on meaningful work by eliminating tedious tasks.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case Studies Grid -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-20">
      
      <!-- Case Study 1: Manufacturing Company -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 space-y-6">
            <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-donut-light-pink rounded-full text-donut-dark-pink font-semibold text-sm">
              PROCESS AUTOMATION
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-800">
              Manufacturing Efficiency Revolution
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              A mid-sized manufacturing company was drowning in manual inventory tracking and quality control reporting. Their team spent 15+ hours weekly on repetitive data entry tasks.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800">The Challenge</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-pink rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Manual inventory tracking across multiple locations</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-pink rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Time-consuming quality control documentation</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-pink rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Error-prone manual data entry processes</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800">The Solution</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We developed an integrated automation system that connected their existing equipment sensors to a centralized dashboard, automatically generating reports and alerts.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-pink">15hrs</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Weekly time saved</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-cyan">95%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Error reduction</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-moss">100%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Team satisfaction</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-donut-light-pink to-donut-light-cyan flex items-center justify-center p-12">
            <div class="text-center space-y-6">
              <div class="text-8xl animate-float">üè≠</div>
              <div class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800">
                Smart Manufacturing
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Case Study 2: Marketing Agency -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="lg:order-2 p-8 lg:p-12 space-y-6">
            <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-donut-light-cyan rounded-full text-donut-dark-cyan font-semibold text-sm">
              CUSTOM APPLICATION
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-800">
              Creative Agency Workflow Transformation
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              A growing marketing agency struggled with project management chaos. Creative teams were spending more time on administrative tasks than actual creative work.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800">The Challenge</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-cyan rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Fragmented project tracking across multiple tools</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-cyan rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Manual time tracking and billing processes</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-cyan rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Difficulty in resource allocation and capacity planning</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800">The Solution</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We built a unified project management platform that integrates creative workflows, automated time tracking, and intelligent resource allocation.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-cyan">40%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">More creative time</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-pink">25%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Revenue increase</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-moss">0</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Missed deadlines</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="lg:order-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-donut-light-cyan to-donut-light-moss flex items-center justify-center p-12">
            <div class="text-center space-y-6">
              <div class="text-8xl animate-float">üé®</div>
              <div class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800">
                Creative Freedom
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Case Study 3: Healthcare Practice -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 space-y-6">
            <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-donut-light-moss rounded-full text-donut-dark-moss font-semibold text-sm">
              SYSTEM INTEGRATION
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-800">
              Healthcare Practice Streamlining
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              A multi-location healthcare practice was losing valuable patient care time to fragmented systems and manual coordination between departments.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800">The Challenge</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-moss rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Disconnected scheduling and patient management systems</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-moss rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Manual insurance verification and billing</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-donut-moss rounded-full"></span>
                  <span>Redundant data entry across multiple platforms</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-800">The Solution</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                We created a unified system that connects all practice management tools, automates routine tasks, and provides real-time insights into practice operations.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-moss">3hrs</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Daily admin time saved</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-cyan">30%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">More patient time</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-donut-dark-pink">99%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Staff satisfaction</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-donut-light-moss to-donut-light-pink flex items-center justify-center p-12">
            <div class="text-center space-y-6">
              <div class="text-8xl animate-float">üè•</div>
              <div class="text-xl font-display font-semibold text-gray-800">
                Patient-First Care
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results Summary -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center space-y-4 mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-800">
          Proven Impact Across Industries
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our human-centered approach consistently delivers measurable results that matter.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center space-y-2">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-donut-dark-pink">50+</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">Hours Saved Weekly</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center space-y-2">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-donut-dark-cyan">95%</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600">Error Reduction</div>
